quotes.quote: She's everything, even when she's treated like nothing.

quotes.quote: and sometimes you have to die just a little bit inside before you truly understand how to live.

quotes.author: A.A. Milne

quotes.quote: She who sets her standards high will never have to settle for less.
quotes.author: Sorella

quotes.quote: The moment you think you can't is when you must believe you can.
quotes.author: Henry Ford

quotes.quote: You're like a grey sky. You're beautiful, even though you don't want to be.
quotes.author: Jasmine Warga
